constraints_details.constraints_layer_description: Canal and River Trust statutory consultee notified area

description: Notification from LLDC of application 24/00244/LBC for Listed Building Consent for the installation cladding along the L-shaped boundary wall together with the wall that extends 90 degrees from it to match the adjacent Aviary Building, including the removal of the benches that were installed into the boundary wall, to prevent children from climbing into the covered area roof space.
